603
00:27:00,159 --> 00:27:02,000
and they could make millions a month.

604
00:27:03,000 --> 00:27:03,839
Just their lies.

605
00:27:04,319 --> 00:27:05,480
Once you join them,

606
00:27:05,559 --> 00:27:06,520
you'd get ripped off.

607
00:27:06,960 --> 00:27:07,760
So,

608
00:27:07,920 --> 00:27:08,399
later,

609
00:27:08,440 --> 00:27:10,000
when we're in there,

610
00:27:10,440 --> 00:27:11,319
we must keep our minds

611
00:27:11,319 --> 00:27:12,440
sober.

612
00:27:13,079 --> 00:27:14,520
Let their words go in one ear

613
00:27:14,639 --> 00:27:15,879
and out the other.

614
00:27:15,960 --> 00:27:16,599
Got it?

615
00:27:17,639 --> 00:27:18,720
Mom, don't worry.

616
00:27:18,839 --> 00:27:20,079
How could we be fooled

617
00:27:20,159 --> 00:27:21,200
by that slow-witted Yu Ming?

618
00:27:22,559 --> 00:27:24,119
You can't be too careful.

619
00:27:24,760 --> 00:27:25,200
Yeah.

620
00:27:25,240 --> 00:27:26,799
Let's first go in to see.

621
00:27:33,079 --> 00:27:34,240
Are the dishes gorgeous enough?

622
00:27:35,599 --> 00:27:36,680
Really gorgeous.

623
