That won't do.

646
00:28:19,639 --> 00:28:20,359
Ming, they should come.

647
00:28:20,399 --> 00:28:22,000
I'll call her right away.

648
00:28:22,159 --> 00:28:23,040
Your mom,

649
00:28:23,079 --> 00:28:23,760
in her whole life,

650
00:28:23,920 --> 00:28:24,879
