652
00:28:25,960 --> 00:28:26,599
Well...

653
00:28:26,639 --> 00:28:28,079
Just don't call her.

654
00:28:28,119 --> 00:28:29,799
We'll have dinner together another day.

655
00:28:30,000 --> 00:28:30,760
Yeah, we had a plan for it.

656
00:28:30,760 --> 00:28:32,040
Let's come together next time.

657
00:28:32,399 --> 00:28:32,960
Yeah.

658
00:28:33,280 --> 00:28:33,760
Yitong,

659
00:28:34,040 --> 00:28:35,399
