662
00:28:37,960 --> 00:28:39,040
You're wearing such a decent outfit.

663
00:28:39,119 --> 00:28:40,240
Is this decent? Just something casual.

664
00:28:40,520 --> 00:28:41,280
Just casual wear.

665
00:28:41,440 --> 00:28:42,240
Y-Yu Ming,

666
00:28:42,359 --> 00:28:43,960
