671
00:28:48,079 --> 00:28:49,000
It's really unnecessary.

672
00:28:49,159 --> 00:28:49,879
It's necessary.

673
00:28:49,879 --> 00:28:50,440
For you two,

674
00:28:50,480 --> 00:28:51,639
in the latter half of the year...

675
00:28:51,839 --> 00:28:52,599
Yeah.

676
00:28:52,879 --> 00:28:53,520
Your daughter

677
00:28:53,599 --> 00:28:55,119
Wenwen's tuition fees

678
00:28:55,159 --> 00:28:56,319
are super high.

679
00:28:56,760 --> 00:28:57,599
Yitong

680
00:28:57,599 --> 00:28:59,440
