I just wanted to treat you to dinner.

684
00:29:03,240 --> 00:29:04,240
I don't believe it.

685
00:29:04,520 --> 00:29:06,359
If you want to take a loan,

686
00:29:06,399 --> 00:29:07,040
I tell you,

687
00:29:07,200 --> 00:29:07,760
