690
00:29:10,200 --> 00:29:11,879
You just can't remember that.

691
00:29:12,079 --> 00:29:13,559
We're not taking a loan, Weijie.

692
00:29:13,799 --> 00:29:14,559
Throughout my life,

693
00:29:14,599 --> 00:29:16,760
I'll never take a loan from you.

694
00:29:16,839 --> 00:29:17,639
I... I invited

695
00:29:17,680 --> 00:29:18,639
