696
00:29:18,680 --> 00:29:19,599
just to enhance

697
00:29:19,639 --> 00:29:21,240
our emotional bonds as relatives.

698
00:29:21,319 --> 00:29:22,200
I know

699
00:29:22,559 --> 00:29:23,879
these years, you might had

700
00:29:23,920 --> 00:29:24,760
some misunderstandings

701
00:29:24,760 --> 00:29:26,119
about our personal development.

702
00:29:26,319 --> 00:29:27,720
I just want to say

703
00:29:27,799 --> 00:29:28,799
that since we're relatives,

704
00:29:28,920 --> 00:29:29,879
there's no need for us

705
00:29:29,879 --> 00:29:31,119
to make a scene

706
00:29:31,119 --> 00:29:32,559
every time we dine together.

707
00:29:32,639 --> 00:29:34,079
Everyone has their dark days.

708
00:29:34,200 --> 00:29:35,119
I want to say

709
00:29:35,280 --> 00:29:37,319
