a case of the most expensive wine.

733
00:30:19,960 --> 00:30:20,879
Sure, please wait a moment.

734
00:30:21,319 --> 00:30:22,240
Bring it bottle by bottle.

735
00:30:23,240 --> 00:30:23,839
Bring more when we're done.

736
00:30:39,760 --> 00:30:40,359
Please enjoy.

737
00:30:41,910 --> 00:30:43,670
(Think bigger)

738
00:30:47,399 --> 00:30:48,040
So pleasant.

739
00:30:51,200 --> 00:30:52,599
Let's drink the pleasant wine, too.

740
00:31:09,440 --> 00:31:10,079
Waitress,

741
00:31:10,799 --> 00:31:11,639
