749
00:31:22,599 --> 00:31:22,960
Come on.

750
00:31:23,200 --> 00:31:23,720
You...

751
00:31:24,760 --> 00:31:25,599
Get up now.

752
00:31:25,879 --> 00:31:27,359
Let's have a drink.

753
00:31:27,720 --> 00:31:29,440
Well, he really can't hold his liquor.

754
00:31:29,680 --> 00:31:31,480
With just these few cups,
you got drunk like this?

755
00:31:38,359 --> 00:31:39,440
Before drinking this,

756
00:31:39,480 --> 00:31:40,599
I'd like to say something.

757
00:31:41,000 --> 00:31:42,359
Today, you...

758
00:31:43,359 --> 00:31:43,799
Well...

759
00:31:43,920 --> 00:31:44,559
Look,

760
00:31:44,799 --> 00:31:46,440
