are a bit out of line.

761
00:31:46,559 --> 00:31:49,200
And you were out of line
on the phone, too.

762
00:31:49,480 --> 00:31:50,119
But

763
00:31:50,920 --> 00:31:52,440
since you're one of our own,

764
00:31:52,760 --> 00:31:54,480
I just won't hold it against you.

765
00:31:55,159 --> 00:31:56,879
But I have to remind you

766
00:31:57,079 --> 00:31:59,319
