when you are out there.

767
00:31:59,639 --> 00:32:00,760
You can be useless.

768
00:32:01,040 --> 00:32:02,319
But you can't be

769
00:32:02,639 --> 00:32:04,960
arrogantly useless.

770
00:32:07,119 --> 00:32:07,639
Yu Ming,

771
00:32:07,839 --> 00:32:08,960
I've said so much

772
