773
00:32:10,280 --> 00:32:12,000
I'm your brother.

774
00:32:12,359 --> 00:32:14,760
Don't just call me by my name.

775
00:32:14,799 --> 00:32:15,359
Okay?

776
00:32:15,879 --> 00:32:16,639
Let me say something too.

777
00:32:17,440 --> 00:32:18,000
I know

778
00:32:18,159 --> 00:32:20,520
