779
00:32:20,639 --> 00:32:22,839
All these years, I've been

780
00:32:23,240 --> 00:32:25,520
at your beck and call.

781
00:32:25,680 --> 00:32:28,319
The reason why I just bore it all
without losing my temper

782
00:32:28,480 --> 00:32:29,839
was that

783
00:32:29,879 --> 00:32:31,680
when my brother passed away,

784
00:32:32,280 --> 00:32:33,559
you helped our family.

785
00:32:35,680 --> 00:32:36,720
When my mom was sick,

786
00:32:37,119 --> 00:32:37,799
my aunt

787
00:32:38,760 --> 00:32:40,520
bought medicine for her from abroad.

788
00:32:41,119 --> 00:32:42,200
And you remember

789
00:32:42,280 --> 00:32:43,159
Wenwen's birthday every year.

790
00:32:43,440 --> 00:32:44,040
I'm very grateful to you.

791
00:32:44,399 --> 00:32:45,879
But I want to tell you

792
00:32:46,159 --> 00:32:47,159
that everyone

793
00:32:47,720 --> 00:32:49,119
can have further development.

794
00:32:49,599 --> 00:32:52,000
I won't just let things go around.

795
00:32:53,200 --> 00:32:53,839
Drink it up.

796
00:33:00,960 --> 00:33:02,359
Weijie, don't drink like that.

797
00:33:05,480 --> 00:33:06,040
Look closely.

798
00:33:08,720 --> 00:33:10,000
This is for the candied hawthorn

799
00:33:10,119 --> 00:33:11,119
I licked

800
00:33:11,480 --> 00:33:12,040
when we were little.

801
00:33:12,839 --> 00:33:14,599
This is for your headset,

802
00:33:14,960 --> 00:33:15,520
broken by me.

803
00:33:16,399 --> 00:33:18,200
This is for breaking

804
00:33:18,960 --> 00:33:20,399
or scratching

805
00:33:21,319 --> 00:33:22,040
your porn DVDs.

806
00:33:22,559 --> 00:33:23,359
There's more.

807
00:33:28,599 --> 00:33:29,799
It's fine.

808
00:33:36,559 --> 00:33:37,760
Let me see

809
00:33:37,799 --> 00:33:39,159
whether the money is genuine.

810
00:33:40,440 --> 00:33:42,040
I-i-is it genuine?

811
00:33:45,680 --> 00:33:46,799
It's genuine.

812
00:33:48,680 --> 00:33:49,720
So much money!

813
00:33:50,480 --> 00:33:52,280
Where did he get all that money?

814
00:33:52,520 --> 00:33:53,079
Look.

815
00:33:53,440 --> 00:33:54,359
It's him.

816
00:33:54,960 --> 00:33:55,639
As far as we know,

817
00:33:55,799 --> 00:33:57,559
Mr. Yu, the lottery winner,

818
00:33:57,760 --> 00:33:59,280
(A lottery buyer won 130 million)
has always been a strong supporter

819
00:33:59,280 --> 00:34:00,520
(A lottery buyer won 130 million)
of the sports lottery.

820
00:34:01,040 --> 00:34:02,480
He's been buying

821
00:34:02,480 --> 00:34:03,319
lottery tickets for ten years.

822
00:34:04,079 --> 00:34:04,920
This outfit,

823
00:34:05,480 --> 00:34:06,720
Mind has an identical one.

824
00:34:07,559 --> 00:34:08,759
Totally the same.

825
00:34:09,719 --> 00:34:10,520
Though before this,

826
00:34:10,520 --> 00:34:11,719
he never won a grand prize,

827
00:34:12,079 --> 00:34:13,239
Mr. Yu thinks

828
00:34:13,360 --> 00:34:14,520
purchasing sports lottery tickets

829
00:34:14,880 --> 00:34:16,599
can not only contribute

830
00:34:16,639 --> 00:34:18,239
to the public welfare undertaking

831
00:34:18,719 --> 00:34:19,840
but also can buy himself...

832
00:34:19,840 --> 00:34:21,320
I also bought a ton of lottery tickets.

833
00:34:21,320 --> 00:34:22,520
Why didn't I win a grand prize?

834
00:34:24,000 --> 00:34:25,040
Having a pipe dream again?

835
00:34:27,559 --> 00:34:29,559
From the winning ticket,
you get 130 million.

836
00:34:29,639 --> 00:34:31,119
There'll be dozens of millions left
after tax deduction.

837
00:34:31,239 --> 00:34:32,639
You might lose it all
by failing your business.

838
00:34:32,679 --> 00:34:33,880
Then you'd owe the bank 130 million.

839
00:34:33,920 --> 00:34:34,480
What's this called?

840
00:34:34,559 --> 00:34:36,599
A sudden fortune would bring disaster.

841
00:34:36,920 --> 00:34:37,360
Think about it.

842
00:34:37,679 --> 00:34:39,199
Even if you become rich,
what can you do?

843
00:34:39,400 --> 00:34:40,800
Live in luxury villas, buy luxury cars.

844
00:34:40,920 --> 00:34:41,759
Every day, you're here

845
00:34:41,759 --> 00:34:43,159
moving luxury cars in and out.

846
00:34:43,159 --> 00:34:44,040
Haven't you had enough of it?

847
00:34:44,159 --> 00:34:45,320
You should know

848
00:34:45,520 --> 00:34:47,599
that buying a luxury car is your dream,

849
00:34:47,840 --> 00:34:48,719
but selling luxury cars

850
00:34:48,719 --> 00:34:50,320
is your true distant goal.

851
00:34:52,000 --> 00:34:52,800
What are you standing there for?

852
00:34:52,880 --> 00:34:53,639
Get moving!

853
00:34:53,639 --> 00:34:55,159
Rush towards your distant goal!

854
00:34:55,480 --> 00:34:56,520
After claiming the prize,

855
00:34:56,679 --> 00:34:58,239
the same afternoon,

856
00:34:58,400 --> 00:34:59,279
Mr. Yu went to the local

857
00:34:59,279 --> 00:35:00,199
