858
00:35:00,480 --> 00:35:01,800
and donated four million

859
00:35:01,960 --> 00:35:03,159
for public welfare,

860
00:35:03,440 --> 00:35:05,000
letting this windfall

861
00:35:05,079 --> 00:35:07,400
bring warmth to society.

862
00:35:07,840 --> 00:35:08,920
Winning the lottery is his luck.

863
00:35:09,159 --> 00:35:10,520
Donating the money shows his true class.

864
00:35:10,599 --> 00:35:11,119
Yu Ming?

865
00:35:11,119 --> 00:35:12,880
Let's congratulate Mr. Yu
on winning the prize again.

866
00:35:13,520 --> 00:35:14,639
That's Yu Ming!

867
00:35:14,679 --> 00:35:15,759
It really is Yu Ming!

868
00:35:15,920 --> 00:35:16,840
Contribute to society.

869
00:35:22,520 --> 00:35:23,159
Well,

870
00:35:23,360 --> 00:35:24,239
Yu Ming has drunk too much.

871
00:35:24,559 --> 00:35:25,480
I'll send him back first.

872
00:35:25,759 --> 00:35:26,440
You guys go on eating.

873
00:35:26,639 --> 00:35:27,559
I'll settle the bill.

874
00:35:28,320 --> 00:35:28,880
Yitong,

875
00:35:29,400 --> 00:35:30,840
I've paid the bill.

876
00:35:30,920 --> 00:35:31,360
Well,

877
00:35:31,559 --> 00:35:33,480
I've put the money back.

878
00:35:34,000 --> 00:35:35,639
If you think the dishes here are good,

879
00:35:36,119 --> 00:35:37,559
we'll come next time.

880
00:35:39,320 --> 00:35:39,719
Yeah.

881
00:35:50,000 --> 00:35:51,820
(Signature: Qian Weijie)

882
00:35:53,599 --> 00:35:55,119
Good thing we changed our clothes back.

883
00:35:55,199 --> 00:35:55,960
You got drunk and might

884
00:35:55,960 --> 00:35:56,840
ruin your clothes by throwing up.

885
00:35:57,759 --> 00:35:59,599
Weijie was so strange.

886
00:35:59,639 --> 00:36:01,040
Why did he compete to pay the bill?

887
00:36:01,079 --> 00:36:01,759
He shouldn't have.

888
00:36:01,759 --> 00:36:02,719
Did he suddenly grow a conscience?

889
00:36:03,400 --> 00:36:04,360
When did he ever have a conscience?

890
00:36:04,759 --> 00:36:05,800
Moreover, his conscience

891
00:36:05,800 --> 00:36:06,880
isn't worth 30,000 at all.

892
00:36:09,159 --> 00:36:10,239
Has he been stunned

893
00:36:10,239 --> 00:36:11,360
by your bragging words?
And he believed it?

894
00:36:11,679 --> 00:36:12,279
That shouldn't be.

895
00:36:12,520 --> 00:36:13,400
Working at the bank,

896
00:36:13,400 --> 00:36:13,960
he must have seen

897
00:36:13,960 --> 00:36:15,480
much of the world.

898
00:36:15,719 --> 00:36:16,759
Darling, do you think he has

899
00:36:17,079 --> 00:36:18,719
found out about our money?

900
00:36:18,960 --> 00:36:19,279
So...

901
00:36:19,480 --> 00:36:20,599
It shouldn't be.

902
00:36:20,719 --> 00:36:21,599
He can't possibly know it.

903
00:36:21,599 --> 00:36:22,480
How could he know it?

904
00:36:22,520 --> 00:36:23,440
This is just so strange.

905
00:36:23,440 --> 00:36:24,599
Their whole family acted weirdly.

906
00:36:24,599 --> 00:36:25,840
They were so arrogant
when they showed up.

907
00:36:25,840 --> 00:36:27,079
Why did they suddenly
change their attitude?

908
00:36:28,360 --> 00:36:28,719
Yu Ming.

909
00:36:31,079 --> 00:36:31,520
Yu Ming,

910
00:36:32,119 --> 00:36:32,960
I'm talking to you.

911
00:36:32,960 --> 00:36:34,520
Let's analyze this a bit.

912
00:36:38,639 --> 00:36:40,559
Good dishes and wine are so expensive.

913
00:36:41,199 --> 00:36:42,520
I have no luck in enjoying them.

914
00:36:42,520 --> 00:36:43,599
I threw it all up.

915
00:36:46,759 --> 00:36:47,759
You're so pathetic.

916
00:36:47,759 --> 00:36:48,920
I'm truly impressed.

917
00:36:49,559 --> 00:36:50,840
Don't bend your neck like that.

918
00:36:51,880 --> 00:36:52,719
Or you just lie down.

919
00:36:54,440 --> 00:36:55,000
Darling,

920
00:36:55,719 --> 00:36:57,480
take me to have some satay noodles.

921
00:36:57,719 --> 00:36:58,759
To nourish myself a bit.

922
00:36:58,920 --> 00:37:00,239
♪I want to get rich♪

923
00:37:00,880 --> 00:37:02,520
(Hong Jinkui)
♪A villa by the sea♪

924
00:37:02,679 --> 00:37:04,079
(Hong Jinkui)
♪Seafood every day♪

925
00:37:04,440 --> 00:37:05,920
♪Fancy cars, pick what I want.♪

926
00:37:06,159 --> 00:37:07,360
That's 130 million!

927
00:37:08,239 --> 00:37:09,360
Oh, my god!

928
00:37:10,000 --> 00:37:12,079
How long can someone spend it all?

929
00:37:12,119 --> 00:37:12,559
Mom,

930
00:37:12,639 --> 00:37:14,480
it's impossible for him
to give it all to us.

931
00:37:14,920 --> 00:37:16,079
At least, he should give us

932
00:37:16,079 --> 00:37:16,960
half of it.

933
00:37:17,159 --> 00:37:19,199
If you ask me,

934
00:37:19,480 --> 00:37:21,599
don't go see

935
00:37:21,719 --> 00:37:22,599
that 130-square-meter apartment.

936
00:37:23,119 --> 00:37:24,840
It's second hand,
and it's not located in a good place.

937
00:37:25,040 --> 00:37:27,040
Better consider the one in Haicang Bay.

938
00:37:27,079 --> 00:37:28,719
Big penthouse in an affluent area.

939
00:37:28,920 --> 00:37:31,360
Four bedrooms, two living rooms,
and two bathrooms.

940
00:37:31,599 --> 00:37:32,719
When the baby is born,

941
00:37:32,719 --> 00:37:33,800
it'll be spacious enough.

942
00:37:34,079 --> 00:37:35,960
We'll check that one tomorrow.

943
00:37:37,159 --> 00:37:37,559
Dad,

944
00:37:37,559 --> 00:37:39,239
your mindset is lagging
behind the times.

945
00:37:39,440 --> 00:37:40,800
Look, house prices are so high now.

946
00:37:40,880 --> 00:37:42,199
There's just no room for appreciation.

947
00:37:42,440 --> 00:37:44,400
You've got to put the money in my hands.

948
00:37:44,599 --> 00:37:46,279
I'm a professional
in financial management.

949
00:37:46,759 --> 00:37:47,320
Enough.

950
00:37:47,440 --> 00:37:48,880
Have you forgotten how much

951
00:37:48,880 --> 00:37:49,679
you've lost in the stock market?

952
00:37:49,960 --> 00:37:50,599
If you ask me,

953
00:37:50,679 --> 00:37:51,599
our family's money

954
00:37:51,759 --> 00:37:52,639
should be managed by me.

955
00:37:53,199 --> 00:37:54,840
If you let me keep the money,

956
00:37:54,880 --> 00:37:55,840
it would be the safest.

957
00:37:56,040 --> 00:37:57,719
I seldom spend money.

958
00:37:57,880 --> 00:37:59,079
I can keep it safe.

959
00:37:59,159 --> 00:38:01,119
Cut it out!

960
00:38:01,320 --> 00:38:02,920
Look at the pile

961
00:38:02,920 --> 00:38:03,719
of those

962
00:38:03,920 --> 00:38:05,679
health supplements.

963
00:38:05,679 --> 00:38:07,279
All fake goods.

964
00:38:07,440 --> 00:38:08,040
If the money

965
00:38:08,279 --> 00:38:09,239
is in your hands,

966
00:38:09,400 --> 00:38:10,759
sooner or later,

967
00:38:10,759 --> 00:38:12,159
those fraudsters will

968
00:38:12,199 --> 00:38:13,239
scam you out of your money.

969
00:38:14,279 --> 00:38:14,960
Qian Lai,

970
00:38:15,279 --> 00:38:16,520
I've married you

971
00:38:16,559 --> 00:38:18,000
for over 40 years now.

972
00:38:18,320 --> 00:38:19,880
Today, I finally

973
00:38:19,880 --> 00:38:21,759
see your true colors.

974
00:38:22,159 --> 00:38:22,679
Enough.

975
00:38:23,000 --> 00:38:23,800
Everyone, stop talking.

976
00:38:24,079 --> 00:38:25,079
Let me tell you,

977
00:38:25,199 --> 00:38:26,040
without my permission,

978
00:38:26,079 --> 00:38:27,639
no one can touch

979
00:38:27,840 --> 00:38:29,400
this money.

980
00:38:32,320 --> 00:38:33,040
What does she mean?

981
00:38:33,119 --> 00:38:34,679
She means she'll keep all the money?

982
00:38:34,840 --> 00:38:36,040
Let me tell you, Qian Weijie,

983
00:38:36,199 --> 00:38:37,040
it was your family

984
00:38:37,040 --> 00:38:37,679
who begged me

985
00:38:37,679 --> 00:38:38,480
for this second child.

986
00:38:38,559 --> 00:38:39,679
Now, your whole family is ganging up

987
00:38:39,679 --> 00:38:40,279
against me.

988
00:38:40,559 --> 00:38:41,440
Let's just call it quits.

989
00:38:41,599 --> 00:38:42,279
I'll take Zihan away,

990
00:38:42,360 --> 00:38:43,279
and you can't see our second baby.

991
00:38:43,759 --> 00:38:44,880
Just live your own days.

992
00:38:56,559 --> 00:38:57,079
Jie,

993
00:38:57,559 --> 00:38:58,920
I think

994
00:38:59,480 --> 00:39:00,159
it's best

995
00:39:00,800 --> 00:39:02,480
to let me keep the money.

996
00:39:02,759 --> 00:39:04,119
I've always been

997
00:39:04,159 --> 00:39:05,239
very reliable.

998
00:39:06,159 --> 00:39:06,840
Where are you going?

999
00:39:07,320 --> 00:39:08,320
I'm buying some cigarettes.

1000
00:39:14,400 --> 00:39:15,520
He's out of his mind.

1001
00:39:17,520 --> 00:39:18,880
Bill validator.

1002
00:39:19,400 --> 00:39:20,559
And there are two of them.

1003
00:39:21,679 --> 00:39:22,119
Gosh.

1004
00:39:22,400 --> 00:39:23,400
How much money could they have?

1005
00:39:25,320 --> 00:39:26,279
If there's really

1006
00:39:26,719 --> 00:39:27,520
nothing important in Unit 505,

1007
00:39:28,159 --> 00:39:28,920
why is that couple

1008
00:39:29,199 --> 00:39:30,000
staying there?

1009
00:39:30,400 --> 00:39:31,239
The villa is full of garbage.

1010
00:39:32,159 --> 00:39:34,000
Yu Ming acted all sneaky.

1011
00:39:34,360 --> 00:39:36,400
He sealed the windows
and changed the lock.

1012
00:39:37,360 --> 00:39:39,360
His wife fighting with him is now back.

1013
00:39:40,480 --> 00:39:41,239
All this shows

1014
00:39:41,880 --> 00:39:42,360
the money

1015
00:39:42,719 --> 00:39:43,800
is right in Unit 505.

1016
00:39:46,000 --> 00:39:47,480
Shall we

1017
00:39:47,880 --> 00:39:49,960
test the waters when it's still dark?

1018
00:39:50,040 --> 00:39:50,520
We can't.

1019
00:39:53,159 --> 00:39:54,440
The surveillance system

1020
00:39:54,440 --> 00:39:55,159
was upgraded last time.

1021
00:39:55,159 --> 00:39:56,199
Now, it's facial recognition.

1022
00:39:56,759 --> 00:39:57,759
Strangers would trigger an alarm.

1023
00:39:59,239 --> 00:40:00,880
Truly a high-end community.

1024
00:40:01,119 --> 00:40:02,719
But we just have to find a way
to sneak in.

1025
00:40:12,880 --> 00:40:15,320
A thousand-mile quest
for the dragon's path,

1026
00:40:16,840 --> 00:40:20,279
where every encircling peak
is a hidden gate.

1027
00:40:22,119 --> 00:40:23,360
What does it mean?

1028
00:40:28,199 --> 00:40:28,719
Dig a hole.

1029
00:40:33,639 --> 00:40:34,320
Get up quickly.

1030
00:40:34,320 --> 00:40:35,840
You'd sleep a full 24 hours
if you continued.

1031
00:40:37,000 --> 00:40:38,199
I'll lie here a while longer.

1032
00:40:39,639 --> 00:40:41,119
Why did you drink with them

1033
00:40:41,119 --> 00:40:41,920
so heavily?

1034
00:40:41,920 --> 00:40:42,880
Don't you know

1035
00:40:42,920 --> 00:40:44,119
your capacity?

1036
00:40:44,360 --> 00:40:45,960
That was fine wine.

1037
00:40:47,119 --> 00:40:49,000
It's over 10,000 a bottle
at Elegant Garden.

1038
00:40:49,000 --> 00:40:50,679
How could I let them drink more
than I did?

1039
00:40:50,719 --> 00:40:51,320
However expensive it is,

1040
00:40:51,320 --> 00:40:52,279
didn't you throw it all up in the end?

1041
00:40:52,279 --> 00:40:52,920
What you threw up

1042
00:40:52,920 --> 00:40:54,000
in the end wasn't that wine,

1043
00:40:54,000 --> 00:40:54,960
but the satay noodles.

1044
00:40:54,960 --> 00:40:56,239
You're just fated to eat satay noodles.

1045
00:40:56,480 --> 00:40:57,279
But it was fine.

1046
00:40:57,400 --> 00:40:59,360
Fine wine doesn't make you
feel so awful.

1047
00:40:59,559 --> 00:41:00,199
Look at this.

1048
00:41:00,840 --> 00:41:02,679
Bought it on a whim.
What's this? A turtle shell?

1049
00:41:02,679 --> 00:41:03,239
It's pretty.

1050
00:41:03,239 --> 00:41:04,239
Can I even go out wearing this?

1051
00:41:04,239 --> 00:41:05,520
Sure, you can. It's not out of place.

1052
00:41:05,520 --> 00:41:06,119
Look at this.

1053
00:41:06,679 --> 00:41:07,159
If I'm wearing these,

1054
00:41:07,159 --> 00:41:08,079
I'd have to practice how to walk.

1055
00:41:08,159 --> 00:41:09,360
I want to return

1056
00:41:09,360 --> 00:41:09,840
all this stuff.

1057
00:41:09,840 --> 00:41:10,520
Why?

1058
00:41:10,679 --> 00:41:11,880
We still don't know

1059
00:41:11,880 --> 00:41:12,719
the origin of the money.

1060
00:41:12,719 --> 00:41:14,440
I just feel insecure
after spending so much

1061
00:41:14,440 --> 00:41:15,239
all at once.

1062
00:41:15,320 --> 00:41:16,440
It has no origin.

1063
00:41:16,440 --> 00:41:17,360
Understand?

1064
00:41:17,440 --> 00:41:18,599
It was found in our house,

1065
00:41:18,639 --> 00:41:19,559
so it's ours.

1066
00:41:19,759 --> 00:41:21,040
It's a gift from heaven.

1067
00:41:21,119 --> 00:41:22,239
Why feel insecure?

1068
00:41:22,440 --> 00:41:23,119
I'll return them all.

1069
00:41:23,199 --> 00:41:23,840
I'll keep none of them.

1070
00:41:23,840 --> 00:41:24,679
I must return them all.

1071
00:41:24,719 --> 00:41:25,559
Return them all?

1072
00:41:25,639 --> 00:41:27,159
Would the salesperson beat us?

1073
00:41:27,279 --> 00:41:27,880
The salesperson...

1074
00:41:29,480 --> 00:41:30,559
Coming!

1075
00:41:31,679 --> 00:41:32,599
Who is it?

1076
00:41:34,480 --> 00:41:35,759
Coming!

1077
00:41:39,159 --> 00:41:40,000
Auntie, you're at home.

1078
00:41:40,159 --> 00:41:40,840
You are...

1079
00:41:40,840 --> 00:41:41,759
It's me, Jie.

1080
00:41:41,920 --> 00:41:42,559
Qian Weijie.

1081
00:41:42,759 --> 00:41:44,000
When Ming and Yitong got married,

1082
00:41:44,000 --> 00:41:44,920
I offered you a toast.

1083
00:41:45,000 --> 00:41:45,559
You don't remember?

1084
00:41:46,880 --> 00:41:47,960
Qian Weijie?

1085
00:41:48,679 --> 00:41:50,119
When was that?

1086
00:41:50,119 --> 00:41:51,520
Did you remember it?

1087
00:41:53,239 --> 00:41:54,159
Why didn't you tell me

1088
00:41:54,159 --> 00:41:55,079
that you had come?

1089
00:41:55,079 --> 00:41:56,040
I would've thrown you a welcome dinner.

1090
00:41:56,360 --> 00:41:57,400
I've brought gifts for you,

1091
00:41:57,480 --> 00:41:58,119
Ming, and Yitong.

1092
00:41:58,279 --> 00:41:59,639
This is black tea

1093
00:41:59,639 --> 00:42:00,800
meant for our bank's key accounts.

1094
00:42:00,840 --> 00:42:01,599
Please try it.

1095
00:42:01,639 --> 00:42:03,040
If you like it, I'll bring you more.

1096
00:42:03,320 --> 00:42:04,840
Ming is not up yet?

1097
00:42:05,040 --> 00:42:06,119
Ming, get up now.

1098
00:42:06,360 --> 00:42:08,000
I've brought you

1099
00:42:08,000 --> 00:42:08,800
an electric razor.

1100
00:42:08,800 --> 00:42:09,599
I tried it. It works great.

1101
00:42:09,639 --> 00:42:10,400
So I bought you one.

1102
00:42:10,559 --> 00:42:11,079
Yitong,

1103
00:42:11,440 --> 00:42:11,960
a gift for you.

1104
00:42:12,239 --> 00:42:12,599
Ya

1105
00:42:12,599 --> 00:42:13,880
has just bought a Tote bag.

1106
00:42:14,000 --> 00:42:14,960
The tag is still on it.

1107
00:42:14,960 --> 00:42:15,840
She says it's very big

1108
00:42:15,880 --> 00:42:16,400
and can fit a lot.

1109
00:42:16,480 --> 00:42:17,360
It would suit you perfectly.

1110
00:42:17,639 --> 00:42:18,400
Come on, get up.

1111
00:42:18,400 --> 00:42:18,840
Get up.

1112
00:42:18,920 --> 00:42:20,040
Get up to look.

1113
00:42:21,199 --> 00:42:22,000
Wenwen, you're here.

1114
00:42:22,639 --> 00:42:23,040
Here.

1115
00:42:24,719 --> 00:42:25,400
I know

1116
00:42:25,400 --> 00:42:26,679
you love snacks of this brand.

1117
00:42:26,800 --> 00:42:27,719
I bought this specially for you.

1118
00:42:27,759 --> 00:42:28,559
Come on, take a look.

1119
00:42:29,639 --> 00:42:30,840
It's too sweet, cloying.

1120
00:42:31,880 --> 00:42:32,320
Wenwen,

1121
00:42:32,360 --> 00:42:33,599
don't you like drawing pictures?

1122
00:42:33,599 --> 00:42:34,599
I happen to know

1123
00:42:34,599 --> 00:42:35,400
a curator.

1124
00:42:35,400 --> 00:42:35,920
I'll have him

1125
00:42:35,920 --> 00:42:36,719
hold a painting exhibition for you.

1126
00:42:36,920 --> 00:42:37,360
How about it?

1127
00:42:40,800 --> 00:42:41,719
Something's off.

1128
00:42:42,000 --> 00:42:43,759
The meal last night cost 37,000.

1129
00:42:45,040 --> 00:42:47,360
37,000? So expensive!

1130
00:42:47,480 --> 00:42:48,199
He covered the bill.

1131
00:42:48,360 --> 00:42:49,119
Why?

1132
00:42:49,159 --> 00:42:49,800
How could I know?

1133
00:42:51,320 --> 00:42:52,480
Let's go out to check it out.

1134
00:42:53,320 --> 00:42:54,079
Let's put on our clothes first.

1135
00:42:58,840 --> 00:42:59,239
Ming,

1136
00:42:59,559 --> 00:43:00,599
how about you deposit that money
with me?

1137
00:43:00,880 --> 00:43:01,599
What money?

1138
00:43:05,080 --> 00:43:07,880
(Next Episode)

1139
00:43:08,239 --> 00:43:09,440
(Actress, Ren Suxi)
I'm Ren Suxi.

1140
00:43:09,559 --> 00:43:11,559
(Actress, Ren Suxi)
I invite you to watch Wonder Wall.

1141
00:43:11,960 --> 00:43:13,719
You won such a huge lottery prize.

1142
00:43:13,759 --> 00:43:14,480
Who would not know?

1143
00:43:14,719 --> 00:43:16,559
You won 130 million!

1144
00:43:16,639 --> 00:43:17,800
Ming, Yitong,

1145
00:43:18,279 --> 00:43:19,800
you two are truly blessed.

1146
